                        <div class="info-section">
                            <div class="info-label">üéØ The Situation</div>
                            <p class="info-text">The customer knows your product, what it does, and wants it‚Äîthey just haven't bought it yet. This is the easiest stage to convert.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="strategy-box">
                            <div class="strategy-label">‚ú® Headline Strategy</div>
                            <p class="strategy-text">Your headline needs to state little more than the <strong>product name and a bargain price</strong>. This is the most "mechanical" form of advertising where the copywriter acts as a "merchandise manager's phrase-maker," and the <strong>price is the most vital element</strong>.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="examples-box">
