                            <p class="strategy-text">You must <strong>name the desire and/or its solution directly and dramatically</strong>. The copywriter must crystallize an amorphous, spreading desire into a <strong>razor-sharp focus</strong>. Don't mention your product name yet‚Äîfocus on the result.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="examples-box">
