                            <div class="info-label">üéØ The Situation</div>
                            <p class="info-text">The prospect has a need but doesn't yet realize that a product can solve it. They feel the pain but don't know relief exists.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="strategy-box">
                            <div class="strategy-label">‚ú® Headline Strategy</div>
                            <p class="strategy-text">Start by <strong>naming the need or problem</strong>, then <strong>dramatize it so vividly</strong> that the prospect realizes they cannot live without the solution. Simple headlines that address a specific future or current problem work best.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="examples-box">
                            <div class="examples-label">üí° Examples</div>
