                            <div class="example-item">"Are You Tired of Being Tired?"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <div class="worksheet-header">
                                <span class="worksheet-icon">‚úçÔ∏è</span>
                                <h4 class="worksheet-title">Your Stage 4 Headline</h4>
                            </div>

                            <div class="worksheet-field">
                                <label class="worksheet-label">What problem/need do they have?</label>
